  ('social-worker-moex-06280', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-104-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者不是質化研究適用的情境：', '["所要研究的環境與文化，事先已有大量資料時", "進入一個很不熟悉的社會系統時", "需描述複雜的社會現象，或案主的主觀理念時", "適於定義一個新概念和形成新的假設"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:33+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5cc1330cfca7", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9dfdf14e60d8", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104100", "c": "107", "s": "0606", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年第二次專技中醫師分階段考試營養師心理師護理師社會工作師考試法醫師語言治療師聽力師牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 36, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-06281', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-104-a62ebd66', 'sub-social-worker-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '在「女性愈感覺到性別平權的職場關係，女性的工作滿意度愈高」這個研究假說中，自變項為何？', '["性別", "職場關係的性別平權程度", "工作滿意度", "職業類型"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:33+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5cc1330cfca7", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9dfdf14e60d8", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "104100", "c": "107", "s": "0606", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作研究方法", "year": "104", "exam_name": "104年第二次專技中醫師分階段考試營養師心理師護理師社會工作師考試法醫師語言治療師聽力師牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 37, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
